                        <h3 class="content">sherelog</h3>
                        <div class="content">
                           <div class="content">
                              <p><img alt="sherelog.jpg" src="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/blogs/setbang/sherelog.jpg" width="260" height="195" /></p>

<p>sherelog is a system that gets information from the japanese rfid enable train passes, suica cards, and visualizes all of the trips onto a large public map [can't seem to find their website though.].  it happens that there is software from sony that allows you to view the train ride records.</p>

