                        <h3 class="content">mobile assassins</h3>
                        <div class="content">
                           <div class="content">
                              <p><img alt="mobile_assassins.gif" src="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/blogs/setbang/mobile_assassins.gif" width="400" height="300" /></p>

<p><a href="http://mobileassassins.com/">mobile assassins</a> is basically a mobile phone version of the assassins games.  everyone playing is given a secret target. once you kill your mark [in this case by snapping a camerphone photo of them] you acquire their hit.  last one standing wins.  although they don't really get into the possibilities - imagine playing this game with total strangers, it could be amazing.</p>

<p>maybe i should work on an urbanized version of mafia... hmmm.</p>
                              
