                                 <span class="post-footers">roxy said on 05:22 PM</span> <span class="separator">|</span> <a class="permalink" href="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/blogs/setbang/2005/07/rabbit_field.html">Permalink</a>
                                 | <a href="http://drzaius.ics.uci.edu/blogs/setbang/2005/07/rabbit_field.html#comments">Comments (0)</a>
                                 
